<item>
            <title>[LU-6886] declare changelog store for POSIX ACLs in mdd_xattr_del</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6886</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;How to reproduce:&lt;br/&gt;
1. enable changelog&lt;br/&gt;
2. on client, write c code which calls&lt;br/&gt;
setxattr(&quot;filename&quot;, &quot;system.posix_acl_default&quot;, val, 0, 0);&lt;br/&gt;
in a loop.&lt;br/&gt;
3. run the c code, make sure it&apos;s the only op issued to mds.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;osd_trans_exec_op() will complain.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should declare changelog store for system.posix_acl_default and system.posix_acl_access.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
